Real-Time Analogy

Imagine a real restaurant:
---------------------------


| Restaurant Department | Flask Project       |
| --------------------- | ------------------- |
| Reception             | `templates/`        |
| Interior Decoration   | `static/css/`       |
| Waiter                | `script.js`         |
| Kitchen               | `app.py`            |
| Chef                  | `gemini_service.py` |
| Billing Counter       | `order_service.py`  |
| Accounts Register     | `google_sheet.py`   |
| Menu Book             | `knowledge/`        |
| Price List            | `data/menu.csv`     |


=====

Each department has a separate responsibility, making the restaurant efficient. A Flask project works the same way.

